### Variables
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/games
@gameId = 1
@sessionId = 1

### Biblioteca de games
GET {{baseUrl}}/library?limit=24
Accept: application/json

### Detalhes do game
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{gameId}}
Accept: application/json

### Detalhes do game por slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/slug/hollow-knight
Accept: application/json

### Busca de games
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=hollow&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Stats globais
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats
Accept: application/json

### Sugestoes IGDB para catalogo
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/suggestions?q=hollow%20knight
Accept: application/json

### Adicionar game ao catalogo via IGDB
POST {{baseUrl}}/catalog
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Hollow Knight",
  "year": 2017,
  "igdbId": "11156"
}

### Adicionar game ao catalogo com entrada minima
POST {{baseUrl}}/catalog
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Celeste",
  "year": 2018,
  "igdbId": null
}

### Registrar sessao jogando
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{gameId}}/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "PLAYING",
  "startedAt": "2026-05-15T20:00:00Z",
  "endedAt": null,
  "notes": "Comecei uma nova campanha."
}

### Registrar backlog
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{gameId}}/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "BACKLOG",
  "startedAt": "2026-05-15T20:00:00Z",
  "endedAt": null,
  "notes": "Entrou na fila para jogar depois."
}

### Registrar finalizado
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{gameId}}/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "startedAt": "2026-05-01T20:00:00Z",
  "endedAt": "2026-05-15T23:00:00Z",
  "notes": "Campanha principal finalizada."
}

### Registrar abandonado
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{gameId}}/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "ABANDONED",
  "startedAt": "2026-05-01T20:00:00Z",
  "endedAt": "2026-05-10T22:00:00Z",
  "notes": "Parei sem intenção de voltar agora."
}

### Remover sessao
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{gameId}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}
Accept: application/json

### Atualizar sessao
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/{{gameId}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "startedAt": "2026-05-16T20:00:00Z",
  "endedAt": "2026-05-21T23:00:00Z",
  "notes": "Campanha finalizada."
}
